    Rehabilitation Updates
  are designed to help track the lifecycle of an asset, specifically the cost and impact of a dedicated rehabilitation
%p During an asset's lifetime, if, for example, a vehicle is overhauled or a building is significantly improved, the relevant information can be recorded here
%p Every time a rehabilitation update is recorded against the asset, the report will be viewable by system users on the asset's timeline, and relevant values for the asset will be recalculated automatically.